se the\n        ``SameSite`` attribute. This currently just returns the value of\n        the :data:`SESSION_COOKIE_SAMESITE` setting.\n","end_line":211,"file_path":"tests/corpus/code/flask/src/flask/sessions.py","kind":"window","language":"python","name":"SessionInterface[2]","similarity":0.8532015085220337,"start_line":172}
